{"tid":543976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海航爆煲】網傳有內銀上周召開海航系業務風險討論會","createTime":"2018-01-29T05:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T18:29:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bf7758fadc2363e86f55ffaeb529e2f38532cc","tid":543976,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180129/s00010/82414889ccecd20b86b60db6fb59c1a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180129%2Fs00010%2F82414889ccecd20b86b60db6fb59c1a4.jpg&h=63b5eb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10間A股公司7間停牌，兼且盛傳已陷周轉不靈的海航系，其資金狀況或已引起銀行關注。近日內地網上流傳一幅圖片，顯示上周四（25日），有內銀發出內部通知，就海航系相關業務召開風險專題討論。<br />\n<br />\n討論內容包括，要求各分行機構匯報各自與海航系的業務情況，包括已上報或未上報，涉及底層資產，或交易對手涉及海航投資業務的情況，以及討論與海航業務相關的風險控制措施。<br />\n<br />\n圖片未有說明召開風險討論的是哪一間銀行，亦沒披露討論結果。據海航過去公布，內地有8大行給予海航授信，包括國開行、中國進出口銀行、中行（3988）、農行（1288）、工行（1398）、建行（0939）、交行（3328）及浦發銀行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1517200984379&amp;issue=20180129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1517200984379%26issue%3D20180129&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=30282aca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1517200984379%26issue%3D20180129&h=c037f964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1517200984379&amp;issue=20180129</a>"},{"pid":"b3b361ec001ffbc76ed3cfb8b4cf6aa5de1583a1","tid":543976,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}